author: David Wiegand
title: ‘Supergirl’ can fly, but not very high
text:
Photo: Sonja Flemming / Sonja Flemming / CBS Melissa Benoist plays the title role in the new CBS series “Supergirl” alongside Chyler Leigh, as her older foster sister, Alex, and David Harewood. Melissa Benoist plays the title role in the new CBS series...
“Supergirl” flies in to the CBS Monday night lineup with a decent pedigree: It was co-created by Greg Berlanti, who is to the CW what Shonda Rhimes is to ABC on Thursday nights.
